1
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:42,440
Scheme.

2
00:01:13,600 --> 00:01:14,600
Strange.

3
00:01:15,640 --> 00:01:17,000
Did I see it wrong?

4
00:01:20,960 --> 00:01:22,760
Your Excellency, please understand.

5
00:01:22,760 --> 00:01:26,360
I came to burn joss paper for my mother-in-law to show my respect.

6
00:01:27,920 --> 00:01:29,960
Your mother-in-law died from heavenly punishment.

7
00:01:29,960 --> 00:01:32,120
She doesn't deserve to receive incense offerings in this holy place.

8
00:01:32,120 --> 00:01:32,920
And you,

9
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:34,800
dare to go out after the bell rings at dark.

10
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:37,200
It's clear you still have lustful thoughts.

11
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:39,000
I will act on behalf of the Holy Maiden

12
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:41,160
to punish you properly.

13
00:01:42,720 --> 00:01:43,759
Stop!

14
00:01:49,360 --> 00:01:50,840
Calm down, my lord.

15
00:01:51,240 --> 00:01:52,759
It's only natural for her

16
00:01:52,759 --> 00:01:54,640
to show filial piety as a daughter-in-law.

17
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:56,840
Breaking the rules once is no big deal.

18
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:57,680
Liu.

19
00:01:57,840 --> 00:01:59,570
You have no right to speak here.

20
00:01:59,800 --> 00:02:01,320
Considering you just arrived today

21
00:02:01,320 --> 00:02:02,800
and your lustful thoughts have not been purged,

22
00:02:02,800 --> 00:02:05,200
I will not punish you for going out after dark.

23
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:07,200
If you break the rules again after taking your vows in seven days,

24
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:08,860
you will be heavily punished.

25
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:11,760
I'm just wondering.

26
00:02:13,160 --> 00:02:15,440
At most, her safety awareness needs to be improved.

27
00:02:15,440 --> 00:02:17,040
How did lustful thoughts get involved?

28
00:02:17,040 --> 00:02:17,840
Your minds...

29
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:19,700
What are you even thinking about?

30
00:02:19,920 --> 00:02:21,050
Going out after dark

31
00:02:21,160 --> 00:02:22,320
not only violates women's virtues,

32
00:02:22,320 --> 00:02:24,180
but also offends the Holy Maiden.

33
00:02:24,320 --> 00:02:25,980
Do you want to be punished too?

34
00:02:27,320 --> 00:02:28,320
Madam,

35
00:02:28,440 --> 00:02:29,960
I failed to follow the rules.

36
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,360
I deserve to be punished.

37
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:33,220
Please don't let me drag you down.

38
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:35,800
My Lord.

39
00:02:36,640 --> 00:02:38,770
I am willing to accept the punishment.

40
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:40,520
Glad you know your place.

41
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:42,360
Your mother-in-law is dead.

42
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:43,720
You have no one to rely on.

43
00:02:43,720 --> 00:02:44,450
You'd better

44
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:46,640
behave yourself.

45
00:02:50,720 --> 00:02:51,720
Lady Liu.

46
00:02:51,920 --> 00:02:53,720
It seems you want to rebel.

47
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:57,440
Calm down, my lord.

48
00:02:57,720 --> 00:02:59,000
If there must be a punishment,

49
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,800
then let it be.

50
00:03:05,640 --> 00:03:06,800
What do you mean?

51
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:08,520
Since a mistake was made,

52
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:10,240
there should be a punishment.

53
00:03:10,720 --> 00:03:12,580
But let's skip the physical pain.

54
00:03:12,720 --> 00:03:14,400
Not only would the Holy Maiden bear not to watch,

55
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:15,920
but it would also cost you energy.

56
00:03:15,920 --> 00:03:17,380
What do you think, my lord?

57
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:19,120
Glad you guys know your place.

58
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:19,800
This time,

59
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:21,320
I'll let it slide.

60
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:24,640
Thank you, my lord.

61
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:29,800
Wow.

62
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:33,360
I think I'm actually getting used to cross-dressing.

63
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:39,520
Thank you, Madam.

64
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:43,640
That militia leader is usually so unreasonable.

65
00:03:44,720 --> 00:03:47,560
If you hadn't helped me today,

66
00:03:47,920 --> 00:03:48,720
I

67
00:03:48,920 --> 00:03:50,720
would definitely have suffered.

68
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:52,200
Unreasonable?

69
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:54,440
That's clearly just an act.

70
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:55,520
Ever since I entered the village,

71
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:56,640
she's been staring at my luggage

72
00:03:56,640 --> 00:03:57,720
and my accessories.

73
00:03:57,720 --> 00:03:59,380
She's obviously very greedy.

74
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:01,520
It's a pity about my silver notes.

75
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:02,760
A whole ten taels.

76
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:10,720
It's getting late.

77
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:12,920
Let me walk you home.

78
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:24,240
So pretty.

79
00:04:36,880 --> 00:04:37,720
Thank you.

80
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:41,320
It seems

81
00:04:41,840 --> 00:04:43,280
you are quite filial.

82
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:46,530
Being filial to parents-in-law is a duty.

83
00:04:46,640 --> 00:04:47,920
You flatter me, Madam.

84
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:50,920
However,

85
00:04:51,320 --> 00:04:53,120
I wonder how your mother-in-law treats you.

86
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:54,720
She is gentle and virtuous.

87
00:04:55,159 --> 00:04:57,520
She treats me like her own daughter.

88
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:08,200
Are these

89
00:05:08,440 --> 00:05:10,300
all made for your mother-in-law?

90
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:13,400
Madam, since you just arrived,

91
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:14,600
you might not know.

92
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:16,640
When she was alive at Lienv Cliff,

93
00:05:16,760 --> 00:05:18,720
my mother-in-law was in charge of funerals.

94
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:21,160
I usually helped her make paper crafts.

95
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,840
Whenever someone passed away,

96
00:05:23,840 --> 00:05:25,320
she had to handle it.

97
00:05:26,520 --> 00:05:29,120
I just didn't expect that this time...

98
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:36,360
Then I won't bother you anymore.

99
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:37,800
I'll be leaving now.

100
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:56,760
A life worse than death

101
00:05:58,520 --> 00:05:59,980
has finally come to an end.

102
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:09,320
Why is Tuanlian here so early?

103
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:23,180
Watch the door.

104
00:06:24,760 --> 00:06:26,520
I used questioning as an excuse to see you.

105
00:06:26,520 --> 00:06:27,780
I shouldn't stay long.

106
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:29,200
I've examined the scene.

107
00:06:30,200 --> 00:06:32,320
The cause of death is very similar to Lady Gu's.

108
00:06:32,320 --> 00:06:34,580
Even the murder weapon might be the same.

109
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:36,460
Are there also signs of drugging?

110
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:40,280
I compared them.

111
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:42,720
The fingerprints on the wine cup at Lady Gu's scene

112
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:43,920
don't belong to Gu Yu.

113
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:45,120
You suspect it's her?

114
00:06:45,520 --> 00:06:46,640
At least according to rumors,

115
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:48,040
they got along well.

116
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:50,320
Being as close as mother and daughter is just a facade.

117
00:06:50,320 --> 00:06:51,180
Moreover, Gu Yu

118
00:06:51,280 --> 00:06:52,440
was obviously abused,

119
00:06:52,440 --> 00:06:54,040
but she deliberately hid it.

120
00:06:54,400 --> 00:06:55,240
Last night,

121
00:06:55,520 --> 00:06:56,920
she was bullied by Tuanlian.

122
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:58,600
This morning, Tuanlian was found dead.

123
00:06:58,600 --> 00:07:00,160
And the cause of death is exactly the same.

124
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:01,520
This is really bizarre.

125
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:02,930
So what should we do now?

126
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:05,440
All of you who came to Lienü Cliff

127
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:06,840
to protect your chastity,

128
00:07:06,840 --> 00:07:09,080
have made a vow before the Holy Maiden.

129
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:10,720
You must strictly observe women's virtues.

130
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:12,120
Purify your hearts and desires.

131
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:12,850
The militia,

132
00:07:12,960 --> 00:07:13,520
Madam Gu,

133
00:07:13,760 --> 00:07:15,560
and the people behind the mountain.

134
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:17,320
They died tragic deaths

135
00:07:17,520 --> 00:07:19,450
because they had impure thoughts.

136
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:22,120
Therefore, the Holy Maiden punished them.

137
00:07:22,320 --> 00:07:24,120
I hope everyone takes this as a warning.

138
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:25,440
Strictly follow the commandments.

139
00:07:25,440 --> 00:07:26,640
Constantly reflect on yourselves.

140
00:07:26,640 --> 00:07:28,840
Do not repeat their mistakes.

141
00:07:31,200 --> 00:07:33,720
Everyone at Lienv Cliff must hand over their money,

142
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:35,980
but the drillmaster hid private wealth.

143
00:07:36,520 --> 00:07:37,720
So the female official concluded

144
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:39,720
that her life was also taken by the Holy Maiden.

145
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:41,720
Using murders to intimidate everyone

146
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:43,450
and force them into submission

147
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,720
is just too much.

148
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:46,400
Using fear

149
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:48,720
is also a way to control people's minds.

150
00:07:49,400 --> 00:07:50,730
In a hellhole like this,

151
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:52,650
how can those living people

152
00:07:52,960 --> 00:07:54,520
possibly stay here?

153
00:07:57,520 --> 00:07:59,240
We will proceed with the original plan.

154
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:00,800
I will investigate in secret.

155
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:01,520
However,

156
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:03,320
this will take forever.

157
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:05,410
We need to find another way.

158
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:06,450
In addition,

159
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:07,720
regarding Lady Gu,

160
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:08,980
I have found new clues.

161
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:30,040
I have rouge and powder in my room.

162
00:09:30,040 --> 00:09:31,640
You can all go and try them.

163
00:09:32,040 --> 00:09:32,840
Okay.

164
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:34,520
Guyu,

165
00:09:35,800 --> 00:09:36,800
come along.

166
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:41,000
Let's go.

167
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:44,800
My Lord.

168
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:47,400
I have some things to confirm,

169
00:09:47,880 --> 00:09:49,520
so I can report back as soon as possible,

170
00:09:49,520 --> 00:09:51,720
and Lienv Cliff will be peaceful again.

171
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:17,440
How was it?

172
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:18,860
Did you have fun today?

173
00:11:20,520 --> 00:11:21,880
I always felt that

174
00:11:22,240 --> 00:11:24,120
being forced into the brothel

175
00:11:24,520 --> 00:11:25,920
was miserable enough.

176
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:27,770
But I didn't expect that

177
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:30,480
those so-called respectable women

178
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:32,880
would live such lowly lives.

179
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:36,480
It's so dull

180
00:11:37,280 --> 00:11:38,740
and they lose themselves.

181
00:11:39,520 --> 00:11:41,240
Seeing them laugh today

182
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:45,120
actually made me feel bad.

183
00:11:46,880 --> 00:11:48,480
They are also constrained by worldly conventions

184
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:49,540
and have no choice.

185
00:11:50,520 --> 00:11:51,320
But I believe

186
00:11:51,800 --> 00:11:53,720
human nature won't be suppressed.

187
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:55,050
Today is the best proof.

188
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:58,880
I can't believe you came up with this trick.

189
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:06,880
I told them

190
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:08,000
to write down

191
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:10,490
the styles they like and find suitable

192
00:12:10,680 --> 00:12:11,320
so that

193
00:12:12,120 --> 00:12:13,380
they can compare them.

194
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:16,400
You are the best.

195
00:12:23,120 --> 00:12:25,450
It's a pity that no matter how witty I am...

196
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:28,210
I can't win Master Liu's heart either.

197
00:12:33,120 --> 00:12:34,200
What are you doing?

198
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:47,170
Why did you change back?

199
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:48,800
You look pretty in women's clothes.

200
00:12:48,800 --> 00:12:49,640
Stop talking.

201
00:12:50,280 --> 00:12:52,680
Why did you call me here in the middle of the night?

202
00:12:52,680 --> 00:12:54,080
Besides investigating the case this time,

203
00:12:54,080 --> 00:12:55,800
there is another important thing.

204
00:12:55,800 --> 00:12:58,000
Gu is responsible for the funerals at Lienv Cliff.

205
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:59,320
After every widow dies,

206
00:12:59,320 --> 00:13:00,600
she buries them herself.

207
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:01,860
She even made a record.

208
00:13:11,640 --> 00:13:11,880
Baicang Haojing,

209
00:13:11,880 --> 00:13:12,080
Wenmo Yinbei.

210
00:13:12,080 --> 00:13:13,280
Why are the names on this

211
00:13:13,280 --> 00:13:14,320
in red and black?

212
00:13:15,520 --> 00:13:17,400
According to the information provided by Prince Jia,

213
00:13:17,400 --> 00:13:18,200
the black ones

214
00:13:18,280 --> 00:13:19,880
are the silver-clothed ones

215
00:13:19,920 --> 00:13:20,400
who died of old age.

216
00:13:20,400 --> 00:13:21,120
The red ones

217
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:22,720
are young women

218
00:13:22,880 --> 00:13:23,940
who died suddenly.

219
00:13:24,480 --> 00:13:25,320
Which is what they call

220
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:26,580
heavenly punishment.

221
00:13:26,920 --> 00:13:29,250
Do you want to verify their cause of death?

222
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:51,960
Excuse me.

223
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:53,000
Sorry to intrude.

224
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:55,130
We also want to help you find the truth.

225
00:13:55,200 --> 00:13:56,200
Let's start here.

226
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:36,200
No autopsy is needed.

227
00:14:36,400 --> 00:14:37,640
I just need to examine the body

228
00:14:37,640 --> 00:14:38,360
to be sure.

229
00:14:49,320 --> 00:14:50,000
It's empty.
